h century, and came to be venerated throughout Europe as a model of a Christian king."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Ermessinde de Montferrer was born about 1135, in France. She had at least 1 son with Raymond De Castelbón-Cerdagne."},"et":{"about 1135–":"umbes 1135–Surnud","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1155–1226":"1155–1226","1135–Female":"1135–Surnud","1226":"1226","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","about 1135":"umbes 1135","France":"Prantsusmaa","Coustouges, Céret, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, France":"Coustouges, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1135–":"noin 1135–Kuollut","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1155–1226":"1155–1226","1135–Female":"1135–Kuollut","1226":"1226","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","about 1135":"noin 1135","France":"Ranska","Coustouges, Céret, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, France":"Coustouges, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1135–":"environ 1135–Décédée","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1155–1226":"1155–1226","1135–Female":"1135–Décédée","1226":"1226","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","about 1135":"environ 1135","France":"France","Coustouges, Céret, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, France":"Coustouges, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, France","lifeSummary":"Ermessinde de Montferrer est née environ 1135, à France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Raymond De Castelbón-Cerdagne."},"de":{"about 1135–":"um 1135–Verstorben","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1155–1226":"1155–1226","1135–Female":"1135–Verstorben","1226":"1226","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","about 1135":"um 1135","France":"Frankreich","Coustouges, Céret, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, France":"Coustouges, Pyrénées-Orientales, Occitanie, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Ermessinde de Montferrer wurde um 1135 in Frankreich geboren. Sie hatte mit Raymond De Castelbón-Cerdagne mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1135–":"about 1135–Desede","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1155–1226":"1155–1226","1135–Fem